iv id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104lrk1665702576500.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lrk1665702576500.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lrk1665702576500.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"lrk1665702576500\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Validate\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines whether the <code class=\"ph codeph\">valerr</code> data processing attribute is added for the selected entity node in the DTD tree. This attribute holds the occurrence or field validation error (depending on whether the selected item is an entity or field). Valid values are <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code> (default).\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lrk1665702576500__p_d5978e1_d5979e1_d5980e1\">This attribute can be inspected using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occproperties</span> for occurrence validation errors or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span> for field validation errors.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lrk1665702576500__section_u3h_p1f_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d985292e69\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"lrk1665702576500__ul_afm_p1f_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrk1665702576500__li_d2987e1_d2988e1_d2989e1\">DTD Entity </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aqg1665702684263.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$occproperties</a><p>Returns or sets the properties of an occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aud1705998763272.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldproperties</a><p>Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529697\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529697\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Validate Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 20, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Validate Determines whether the valerr data processing attribute is added for the selected entity node in the DTD tree. This attribute holds the occurrence or field validation error (depending on whether the selected item is an entity or field). Valid values are True or False (default). This attribute can be inspected using $occproperties for occurrence validation errors or $fieldproperties for field validation errors. Applies To DTD Entity Related Links $occproperties Returns or sets the properties of an occurrence. $fieldproperties Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}